Package:      rtest
Version:      0.5.24
Date:         2011/02/24
Title:        unit and system testing for R
Author:       Matthias Burger <burgerm@users.sourceforge.net>, Klaus Juenemann <k.junemann@gmx.net>, Thomas Koenig <thomas.koenig@epigenomics.com>, Mario Frasca <mfrasca@users.sourceforge.net>
Maintainer:   Mario Frasca <mariotomo@gmail.com>
LazyLoad:     yes
Depends:      R (>= 2.5.0), utils (>= 2.5.0), methods (>= 2.5.0), XML (>= 3.1)
Description:  rtest is a fork from RUnit.  it offers a simple system test suite and this is the only part I really maintain.  it provides xml output that makes integration in Hudson, while coverage reports in unit test results are on its way.
License:      GPL-2
URL:          https://r-forge.r-project.org/projects/rtest/
